metadata.name: Crystal Water Sayo
metadata.description:
This Beauty in a swimsuit is Sayo enjoying the crystal clear water on a sunny day she is perfect for anyone's collection She's waiting for you! 

Voice of Truth

Ocean waves cry out,
From the center of the sea:
With faith to reach land.

真実の声

海の波が叫び、
海の中心から：
大地にたどり着く信念を持って。
